'''{{lang|en|Newgrounds}}'''是一間美國娛樂網站和公司。網站能託管用戶提交的創作內容，例如遊戲、電影、音頻和藝術組合。{{lang|en|Newgrounds}}還提供訪問者對用戶提交的內容投票，並藉此進行排名。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/@SeanBuckelew/newgrounds-64831b97a5a8|title=Newgrounds: Everything by Everyone|last=Buckelew|first=Sean|date=2014-12-27|website=Sean Buckelew|access-date=2018-04-21|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110184908/https://medium.com/@SeanBuckelew/newgrounds-64831b97a5a8|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該網站的所有者湯姆·富爾普（{{lang|en|Tom Fulp}}）創辦了網站，並於1995年在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]{{le|格倫賽德 (賓夕法尼亞州)|Glenside, Pennsylvania|格倫賽德}}成立總部和辦事處。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cheltenhamtownship.org/businessdirectory/business_dir.htm#N|title=Cheltenham Township Business Directory|date=January 2007|accessdate=2008-11-20|archive-date=2010-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328174142/http://www.cheltenhamtownship.org/businessdirectory/business_dir.htm#N|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自2006年以來，{{lang|en|Newgrounds}}的口號是「一切，每個人（{{lang|en|Everything, By Everyone}}）」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.newgrounds.com/ |title=Newgrounds.com — Everything, By Everyone |access-date=2019-01-01 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208051629/https://www.newgrounds.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在1995年到2006年間則是「未來的問題，就在今天！（{{lang|en|The Problems Of The Future, Today!}}）」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newgrounds.com/wiki/about-newgrounds/history|title=Newgrounds Wiki - History|website=Newgrounds|access-date=2019-02-18|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208052044/https://www.newgrounds.com/wiki/about-newgrounds/history|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newgrounds.com/ |title=Newgrounds.com — The Problems Of The Future, Today! |access-date=2020-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060209041725/http://newgrounds.com/ |archive-date=2006-02-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》雜誌在2010年的「五十大網站」名單中將{{lang|en|Newgrounds}}名列第39位<ref>{{Cite magazine|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2012721_2012922_2012919,00.html|title=50 Best Websites 2010 - TIME|author=TIME Staff|date=2010-08-25|magazine=Time|access-date=2019-08-18|issn=0040-781X|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213235354/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2012721_2012922_2012919,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

